# New app. New Us.

Let’s GET

INTO IT

Welcome to our second act.

[Get the New App](https://eventbrite.app.link/get-the-app-mlp)

Meet the new Eventbrite App

It’s everything you want to get into… right in one place. Find more new things to do with a personalized feed and insider guides from our culture curators.   
  
Book with confidence thanks to new key event details that let you understand the vibe before booking. Share events with friends, and find out first when they’ve booked.  
‍  
With our new app, it’s easy to get into going out.

Find it.

There's more new things to do.

Discover exciting experiences

Our discover tab is now your personalized feed, with custom recommendations and more search and filtering options to inspire your next adventure.

Explore It-Lists: our curated guides

Discover exciting and unexpected things going on in your city with It-Lists: hand-picked happenings from local culture curators. Launching in select cities but coming to more markets soon.

Ready to get into it?

[Get the New App](https://eventbrite.app.link/get-the-app-mlp)

Book it.

Commit with confidence.

Have that good-to-know event info

Our updated event listings provide key details and highlights so you can feel good about locking in your plans.

Vibe check before checkout

With superior photos and videos of locations and events, you’ll get a sense for the scene before buying your tickets.

Share it.

And see what everyone’s got going on.

Find and follow friends

Seamlessly import contacts and find your friends, so you can share your finds and always stay looped in on the latest and greatest happenings.

See who's   
booked

Let FOMO be a bygone. See first when friends have booked and never miss a plan you want to be a part of.

Get into It.

Everything you need, right in one place.

Always have tickets on-hand

Have all your tickets in a dedicated tab, or saved to your phone wallet, so you’re never searching (or printing).

And details at your fingertips

Address, time, parking info—always be prepared with the last-minute info you need.

Four easy

Tabs

Our app is organized into four main tabs for a simple-to-navigate experience.

Discover

Recommended events, culture curated It-Lists, with more filtering options and better visuals so you can find and commit to your next adventure.

Saved

Never lose track of your best-laid plans or It-Lists that caught your eye. Share them from here with friends to make coordinating more fun.

Tickets

Have your tickets and all those important last-minute event details right at your fingertips.

Account

Find and add friends, manage followers, update your profile.

Ready to get into it?

Download the app and start discovering events like never before. Your next adventure is waiting
